Healthcare, aerospace, automotive, and telecommunications industries are major drivers of the fiber optic probe market.

4. What are the technological advancements in fiber optic probes?

Recent advancements include enhanced performance, miniaturization, and cost reductions, improving their integration into various applications.

5. How does fiber optic technology benefit the medical field?

