Fiber optic probes are crucial for non-intrusive, real-time monitoring of industrial systems, enhancing accuracy and reliability.

9. Are fiber optic probes cost-effective?

While fiber optic probes are initially expensive, their long-term benefits, such as accuracy and durability, often outweigh the costs.

10. How does fiber optic technology enhance performance in sensor systems?

Fiber optic probes offer high sensitivity and resistance to electromagnetic interference, improving the performance of sensor systems.

